        {
            "title": "黃金價格進一步下跌,伊朗談判和美國利率不確定性提振美元",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/FjHV9Ulb4HVCpf_bD6aQJg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXMPEA5N0EK_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com- 黃金價格週四在亞洲交易時段下跌,延續近期跌勢,並短暫跌破近期交易區間,因伊朗戰爭和美國利率的不確定性支撐美元,抑制了對黃金的需求。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">截至美國東部時間23:06(北京時間03:06),現貨黃金下跌0.7%至4,704.96美元/盎司,而黃金期貨下跌0.7%至4,720.11美元/盎司。現貨價格一度跌至4,694.23美元/盎司的低點,跌破過去兩週4,700美元至4,900美元/盎司的交易區間。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-845f5352-770b-3727-9f66-7981e5f64cef-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">由於市場對更多美伊談判的狀況仍存在很大不確定性,黃金難以取得進展,此前總統唐納德·川普無限期延長了停火協議。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在本週計劃的談判基本落空後,德黑蘭和華盛頓對新一輪談判表現出不太開放的態度。伊朗表示,美國必須在任何談判開始前解除對該國的封鎖,而華盛頓則要求完全重新開放霍爾木茲海峽。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">但伊朗繼續封鎖霍爾木茲海峽,而美國則維持對伊朗的海上封鎖,並在更廣泛的亞洲地區監控伊朗船隻,使雙方陷入僵局。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">本週油價飆升至每桶100美元以上,使人們對能源推動通脹的擔憂持續存在。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">金屬市場也受到美元走強的壓力,美元週四穩定在近1週半的高位。在川普提名的聯準會主席人選凱文·沃什表示他沒有承諾降息(如總統所要求的那樣)後,美元走強。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">其他貴金屬週四錄得更深跌幅。現貨白銀下跌2.5%至75.7245美元/盎司,而現貨鉑金下跌1.9%至2,040.16美元/盎司。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%BB%83%E9%87%91%E5%83%B9%E6%A0%BC%E9%80%B2-%E6%AD%A5%E4%B8%8B%E8%B7%8C-%E4%BC%8A%E6%9C%97%E8%AB%87%E5%88%A4%E5%92%8C%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E5%88%A9%E7%8E%87%E4%B8%8D%E7%A2%BA%E5%AE%9A%E6%80%A7%E6%8F%90%E6%8C%AF%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83-041446475.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-23 12:20:50",
