            "title": "停火延長談判未明，亞太早盤油價飆升！布油盤中突破106 美元、WTI 觸及 97",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>Investing.com -</strong>周四，4月23日，今日亞太市場早盤，倫敦布倫特原油期貨一度突破106美元/桶，日內升超4%。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"576\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/wPPaTKwmLdjmPjvnwyAhmQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU3Ng--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/investing_com_hk_986/6bea0992c797a3a06638650082d318da\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">WTI原油期貨同步走高，早盤一度站上97美元。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"579\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/UauUdnssotoH2.wTrYuikw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU3OQ--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/investing_com_hk_986/e9db1797910a6c226ccacd3116de28c1\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">消息面上，美國總統<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"特朗普\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:特朗普;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/特朗普\">特朗普</a>當地時間周二宣佈延長停火期後，美伊新一輪談判的前景仍不明朗。原定巴基斯坦伊斯蘭馬巴德和談未能舉行，霍爾木茲海峽航運基本中斷。以色列媒體稱特朗普設定的停火期截止於26日、即本周日，凸顯了美伊啟動和談化解重開戰事風險的緊迫性。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-7521a773-2b80-367f-a4c3-22d604e701f0-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">\"特朗普延長停火並未帶來真正的確定性，但就目前而言，這對市場已經足夠利好，\"LPL Financial首席技術策略師Adam Turnquist表示，\"風險偏好回來了。\"<br/><br/></p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><blockquote class=\"border-pebble mx-5 my-7.5 border-l-2 pl-5 italic\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-dolphin\"><strong><u><span>快閃倒計時：</span></u></strong><strong><u><span>InvestingPro </span></u></strong><strong><u><span>立享</span></u></strong><strong><u><span>55% </span></u></strong><strong><u><span>折扣！特斯拉財報，一站式查看，助你未雨綢繆，</span></u></strong> <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"即刻點擊訂閱\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:即刻點擊訂閱;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.investing.com/pro/pricing?utm_medium=feed&amp;utm_source=yahoo&amp;utm_campaign=yahoo-hk\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><strong><em><span>即刻點擊訂閱</span></em></strong></a><strong><u><span>！</span></u></strong></p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"364\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/KFaSUyyEoyTSU7Eg9uBr.Q--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTM2NA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/investing_com_hk_986/25ef8faa22e6e8843eecb0829c